ItemTitle: BG Electrical 822BELL Moulded White Round Edge 2 Gang 13A Door Chime Switched Socket
ItemTextDescription:
The BG Electrical Moulded 822BELL is a white double (2 gang) switched socket with door chime, rated at 13A.

Part of the moulded round-edge range, the 822BELL is a great value option for a variety of domestic and office installations. As well as two single pole switched sockets it comes with an integrated door chime function with a battery-operated IP44 (weather-resistant) push button. This chime has a range of up to 100m in open air, has an adjustable volume up to 80dB, so can be heard from anywhere in the house and 6 melodies are provided � 4 �Ding Dong� and 2 �Westminster� style melodies. For no interference, a 1-in-a-million pairing code is randomly generated to each device, and both the socket and button are produced in a white moulded urea which is inherently anti-microbial.

The 822BELL is easy to install, with angled, colour-coded terminals and captive screws making it simply to install into an existing backbox (minimum depth 25mm).

As per the entire 800 range of switches and sockets, the 822BELL comes with a 30 year warranty for peace of mind. It is manufactured to BS 1363 to comply with national building regulations, and a CR2032 battery for the push button is provided.
